%h3
  Roles
  %small{style: 'float: right;'}= link_to 'Create a new role', new_role_path

%p Roles are used to control which volunteers can sign up for certain shifts.  Roles can be based on training, experience etc.

.panel.panel-default
  .table-responsive
    %table.table.table-striped
      %tbody
        %tr
          %th Name
          %th Description
          %th
        - @organization.roles.each do |role|
          %tr
            %td= role.name
            %td= role.description
            %td= link_to 'Edit', edit_role_path(role)
